finished_indicator, cast(registered_date as TIMESTAMP)registered_date, response_id, recipients_last_name, recipients_name, recipients_email, 
external_reference_data, latitude_of_the_location, length_of_location, distribution_channel, users_language, 
nps_rating, cast(nps_score as INTEGER)nps_score, q1, q2, q3, q4, q5, q6, q7, q8, q9, q10, q11, q12, q13, q14, q15, q16, q17, q18, q19,

q39, q40, q41, qid10_9, q5_topics, q8_topics, reason_nps_1, reason_nps_2,
'Y' as actv_rec_ind,
1 as dummy
FROM cdp_stg_dwh.stg_nps_data)src
left outer join
(select 1 as dummy, max(fact_nps_data_key) as MAX_SID from cdp_dwh.fact_nps_data_t) LKP_MAXSID
on src.dummy = LKP_MAXSID.dummy
